com.mingweisamuel.zyra.util

Class LazyResetableFuture<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mingweisamuel.zyra.util.Lazy<T>
      • com.mingweisamuel.zyra.util.LazyResetable<CompletableFuture<T>>
        • com.mingweisamuel.zyra.util.LazyResetableFuture<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompletionStage<T>, Supplier<CompletableFuture<T>>

    public final class LazyResetableFuture<T>
extends LazyResetable<CompletableFuture<T>>
implements CompletionStage<T>
    A Lazy specifically for CompletableFutures with reset functionality. Adds the join() method for convenience.

    Note: Methods implementing CompletionStage keep a reference to the original LazyResetableFuture so they should be used with caution to avoid memory leaks.
